Module io.netty5.common
Package io.netty5.util.concurrent

Interface FutureCompletionStage<V>

  • Type Parameters:
    V - the value type.
    All Superinterfaces:
    CompletionStage<V>
    public interface FutureCompletionStage<V>
extends CompletionStage<V>
    A CompletionStage that provides the same threading semantics and guarantees as the underlying Future, which means that all the callbacks will be executed by executor() if not specified otherwise (by calling the corresponding *Async methods). Please be aware that toCompletableFuture() is not supported and so will throw a UnsupportedOperationException when invoked.
